---
---

<section class="relative py-12 md:py-20 bg-[var(--sd-section-alt-bg)]">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="md:flex items-center gap-8 md:gap-12">
      <div class="md:basis-1/2 mb-8 md:mb-0">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--sd-text)] mb-6 leading-tight">
          Manifesto pela Soberania Digital nas <span class="text-[#45a2ca]">Universidades Públicas Brasileiras</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-[var(--sd-text-2)] mb-4">
          Quem controla o software, o hardware e a conexão de rede controla o mundo digital. As Big Techs têm um enorme interesse na área da educação e elas podem trazer problemas para a soberania nacional e para o desenvolvimento da ciência e da educação brasileira.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-[var(--sd-text-2)] mb-8">
          Precisamos de fomento às ações de desenvolvimento de Inteligências Artificiais que incorporem as cosmovisões dos povos e comunidades que habitam nosso país. Queremos soberania e tecnodiversidade!
        </p>
        <a
          href="/manifesto"
          class="inline-block bg-[#45a2ca] hover:bg-[#3a8ab0] text-white font-bold py-2.5 px-6 md:py-3 md:px-8 text-base md:text-lg transition-colors shadow-lg"
        >
          LEIA O MANIFESTO
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="md:basis-1/2">
        <div class="bg-[var(--sd-card-bg)] p-5 md:p-8 border border-[var(--sd-card-border)]">
          <div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 md:gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 rounded-full bg-[#45a2ca] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-[var(--sd-text)] font-bold text-base md:text-lg">Código Aberto</h3>
                <p class="text-[var(--sd-text-muted)] text-sm md:text-base">Tecnologias baseadas em software livre e aberto</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 md:gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 rounded-full bg-[#45a2ca] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-[var(--sd-text)] font-bold text-base md:text-lg">Soberania Nacional</h3>
                <p class="text-[var(--sd-text-muted)] text-sm md:text-base">Controle democrático sobre dados e algoritmos</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 md:gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 rounded-full bg-[#77b978] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-[var(--sd-text)] font-bold text-base md:text-lg">Tecnodiversidade</h3>
                <p class="text-[var(--sd-text-muted)] text-sm md:text-base">Cosmovisões dos povos e comunidades brasileiras</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
